Lair</EM>.&nbsp;=20
  [0.04 addition; 0.05 some appearance improvement]<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;=20
  <LI>I may as well grab a list of related blogs while I am doing that. =
[0.04=20
  addition; 0.05 some appearance improvement]<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;=20
  <LI>I need to set the sequence on the model I am accustomed to as =
well:=20
  <UL>
    <LI>Description, to be simpler, maybe smaller type=20
    <LI>Atom feed indicator and symbol [0.04 addition]=20
    <LI>Associated Blogs list [0.04 addition]=20
    <LI>Blogger badge [0.04 move]=20
    <LI>Search badge=20
    <LI>Replacement of profile with smaller picture, blogs that link =
here, view=20
    my profile and technorati badge=20
    <LI>ClustrMap [0.04 addition]=20
    <LI>Recent Items [0.04 addition]=20
    <LI>Archive [0.04 change - still need to fix fonts and=20
    appearance]<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </LI></UL>
  <LI>I am self-hosting this blog, so the internationalization of static =

  headings is irrelevant and I can simplify styles further [0.04 =
start]</LI></UL>
<P>I need to be careful and not attempt too much of this all at=20
once.&nbsp;&nbsp; This is going to be one of those pages that I will =
probably=20
update as I make progress.</P>
